OL,3,CAsda fined #0.5m over out-of-date food
OL,4,Cat supermarket
OL,6,FSupermarket giant Asda has been fined
OL,7,F#500,000 for repeatedly displaying out-
OL,8,Fof-date food items for sale at a store
OL,9,Fin Barnsley.
OL,11,FThe Yorkshire-based company pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to five offences under the Food
OL,13,FSafety Act at Barnsley Magistrates
OL,14,FCourt and was ordered to pay #507,767
OL,15,Fin fines and costs.
