OL,6,FA Barnsley Trading Standards
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "While improvements
OL,8,Fhave been made since these offences,
OL,9,Fincluding a new checking system,
OL,10,Fretraining and increased auditing in
OL,11,Fthe store, the sizeable #100,000 fine
OL,12,Fper offence sends a clear message that
OL,13,Fnon-compliance never pays."
OL,15,FCllr Wendy Cain, Barnsley Council's
OL,16,Fpublic health spokesperson, added:
OL,17,F"We're committed to keeping our
OL,18,Fcommunities safe, a responsibility we
OL,19,Ftake very seriously.
