OL,6,F"We expect businesses of all sizes to
OL,7,Fonly sell safe food, and this
OL,8,Fsignificant result sends a clear
OL,9,Fmessage that we will always put
OL,10,Fpeople's health and safety first,
OL,11,Ftaking action where businesses fail to
OL,12,Fcomply with legislation or respond to
OL,13,Fwarnings."
OL,15,FAn Asda spokesperson said: "We are
OL,16,Fdisappointed that some out out-of-date
OL,17,Fproducts were found on sale at our
OL,18,FBarnsley store in 2024.
